
1. SDK 다운로드 
https://software-dl.ti.com/jacinto7/esd/processor-sdk-linux-jacinto7/08_06_01_02/exports/docs/linux/Overview_Getting_Started_Guide.html


2. 빌드 환경 설정
https://software-dl.ti.com/jacinto7/esd/processor-sdk-linux-jacinto7/08_06_01_02/exports/docs/linux/Overview_Building_the_SDK.html


3. 우분투 18.04 에서 아래 명령으로 기본 SDK 빌드
$ . conf/setenv
$ export TOOLCHAIN_BASE=<PATH_TO_TOOLCHAIN>
$ MACHINE=j7-evm bitbake tisdk-default-image


4. GitHub 에서 Gateway 코드 colne
$ git clone https://github.com/AutomotiveNegotiation2/IntelligentGW_SecureECU.git -b gateway


5. 아래 폴더 Tree 와 같이 J7_v2x-mirror 폴더와 meta-v2x 폴더를 기본 설치한 SDK에 복사 

<SDK TOP Folder>
    | ...
    |- J7_v2x-mirror
    |       |- linux-ti-staging
    |       |- ti-rtos-firmware
    |       |- u-boot-ti-staging
    | ...
    |- yocto-build
    |       |- build
    |       | ...
    |       |- sources
    |             |- bitbake
    |             | ...
    |             |- meta-v2x
    |             | ...


6. <SDK TOP Folder>/yocto-build/build/conf/bblayers.conf 파일의 BBLAYERS 항목에 meta-v2x 추가

BBLAYERS += " \
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    <SDK TOP Folder>/yocto-build/sources/meta-aws \
    <SDK TOP Folder>/yocto-build/sources/meta-jupyter \
    <SDK TOP Folder>/yocto-build/sources/meta-v2x \
"


7. <SDK TOP Folder>/yocto-build/build/conf/local.conf 에 아래 추가
MACHINE = "j7-evm"
BBMASK = "/oe-core/meta/recipes-support/curl"

8. Clean 후 재 빌드
$ bitbake tisdk-default-image -c clean 
$ bitbake tisdk-default-image
